            <title>[AVRO-1623] GenericData#validate() of enum: IndexOutOfBoundsException</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/AVRO-1623</link>
                <project id="12310911" key="AVRO">Apache Avro</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When invoking GenericData.get().validate() with a union schema containing multiple record schemas an IndexOutOfBoundsException is possible.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The exception results under the following conditions:&lt;br/&gt;
  1) Union contains multiple record schemas&lt;br/&gt;
  2) The first record schema in the union contains more fields than subsequentrecord schemas&lt;br/&gt;
  3) validate() is invoked with the union schema and a record of one of the&lt;br/&gt;
subsequent record schemas.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
