                            <comment id="14253673" author="nielsbasjes" created="Fri, 19 Dec 2014 17:21:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Other projects have also gotten this:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/pull/331/files&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/pull/331/files&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14253872" author="cutting" created="Fri, 19 Dec 2014 19:33:07 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Niels, do you want to prepare a patch that fixes this?  Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14253993" author="nielsbasjes" created="Fri, 19 Dec 2014 20:44:54 +0000"  >&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;$ find . -type f -print0 | xargs -0 fgrep -i forkMode
./lang/java/pom.xml:            &amp;lt;forkMode&amp;gt;always&amp;lt;/forkMode&amp;gt;
./lang/java/pom.xml:              &amp;lt;forkMode&amp;gt;once&amp;lt;/forkMode&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://maven.apache.org/surefire/maven-surefire-plugin/examples/fork-options-and-parallel-execution.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://maven.apache.org/surefire/maven-surefire-plugin/examples/fork-options-and-parallel-execution.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;div class=&apos;table-wrap&apos;&gt;
&lt;table class=&apos;confluenceTable&apos;&gt;&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;Old Setting	&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;New Setting&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;forkMode=once (default)&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;	forkCount=1 (default), reuseForks=true (default)&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;forkMode=always	&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td class=&apos;confluenceTd&apos;&gt;forkCount=1 (default), reuseForks=false&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14270769" author="nielsbasjes" created="Fri, 9 Jan 2015 08:47:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;@&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=cutting&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;cutting&quot;&gt;Doug Cutting&lt;/a&gt;: Could you please check this patch from just before the holidays. Thanks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
